{"tid":905867,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公斤定義變　棄砝碼改用電磁力秤","createTime":"2018-11-17T13:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T14:15:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"21985123a6def80f200522c271b08d490b92ec4c","tid":905867,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181117/20548093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548093&d=nB5ztyhmxo3RXYuRg1Cq1smDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=c95462df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548093&h=a4c42b83\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181117/20548093</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月17日 <br />\n<br />\n公斤定義變　棄砝碼改用電磁力秤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181117/large/a1206a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181117%2Flarge%2Fa1206a.gif&h=cd5fe458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨天在法國凡爾賽舉行的國際度量衡大會，正式通過改變質量單位公斤的定義方法，由實體改為以物理學常數來定義甚麼是一公斤，是長度、時間、溫度等度量衡公制七大基本單位最後一個擺脫實體定義。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以物理學常數精確計算<br />\n<br />\n自1889年來，想準確量度一公斤，就要拿法國收藏的「國際公斤原器」出來度一度，可是這個被暱稱為「大K」的鉑銥合金標準砝碼，跟世界各地複製品的質量漸見出入，按計算流失了50微克的質量，雖只是一粒沙左右，但在製藥、納米技術和精準工程等追求高準確測量的世界，這樣的誤差已不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n為擺脫標準砝碼實際質量會出現不穩的問題，科學家推動改以物理學常數來定義公斤。透過基布爾秤（Kibble balance）以電流產生的電磁力秤重，由於電流可以準確測量，質量亦可準確計算出來，將是普朗克常數（Planck's constant）的某個倍數，任何有基布爾秤的地方，都可用這統一標準準確量度質量。大會昨天決定除了改變公斤的定義方式，亦一錘定音確認近年實驗測出的普朗克常數詳細數值，但一公斤具體是普朗克常數的多少倍，尚待明年測量後敲定。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n新技術測智障風險　可篩選試管嬰"},{"pid":"e5690d6028d4fae7e40ab4ba3a4ee9035467732f","tid":905867,"uid":53466,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8d9082b21dc2b5f2fe1c9e5efc98af49feb0726","tid":905867,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:06:46.000Z","msg":"關我𨶙事"},{"pid":"cc2449b4ca537cb6c460f1ba41ac8aed13b2d341","tid":905867,"uid":22604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9556e6e3c0f03f1abcd27c01534c100e112471b0","tid":905867,"uid":198583,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"cc2449b4ca537cb6c460f1ba41ac8aed13b2d341","tid":905867,"uid":22604,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:10:26.000Z","msg":"加密好型喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7ca1cbfc2687550e4395a61bb8b01b0011c58c","tid":905867,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:10:55.000Z","msg":"咁啲常數嘅數值係用咩準則嚟定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會變circular statement"},{"pid":"7e26c8991b2d9c14e39f3c5993be9e9b45cf6d79","tid":905867,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160d40e4e3a892fac91302bde912d7ea38ddb884","tid":905867,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:15:58.000Z","msg":"即係好似之前將一秒定義為Caesium atom震唔知幾多萬次既時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc8e8da19f2fba7cce5f1cf52dc3ad362a57dc9","tid":905867,"uid":32996,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T13:27:55.000Z","msg":"睇片仲清楚<br />\n <br /